The '''Royal Hut''', or '''chieftain's hut''', was the home of the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] [[Chief/Legends|chief]] and his family in the [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]] on the Forest Moon of [[Endor/Legends|Endor]].<ref name="Ewoks 1">[[Ewoks (1985) 1|''Ewoks'' (1985) 1]]</ref> It also served as a village meeting-lodge for the chief's [[Bright Tree Village tribe|tribe]].<ref name="GG5">''[[Galaxy Guide 5: Return of the Jedi]]''</ref><ref name="ROTJ Storybook">''[[Return of the Jedi: The Storybook Based on the Movie]]''</ref>

[[Chief/Legends|Chief]] [[Chirpa/Legends|Chirpa]] occupied the chieftain's hut of Bright Tree Village in [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]]. It was here that [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] told the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] village elders the story of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance's]] [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|struggle]] against the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] and where the elders made the [[Endor strike team/Legends|strike team]] a part of the [[Bright Tree Village tribe|tribe]].<ref name="ROTJ" />

